title: [FSX] MegaSceneryEarth - Arizona (1-10)
description:
Fly Arizona in photoreal detail.

Arizona is the fifth largest state in the lower 48 at over 113,998 square miles in size and has 220 airports. You'll see everything that you see in Arizona in real life in the scenery.

Arizona is a visually spectacular and fun place to fly with terrain that varies from towering mountain peaks above 12,500 feet, high plains, canyons, basins, mesas and deserts. This kind of terrain is where MegaSceneryEarth 2.0's high res graphics really shine. You'll be truly stunned by the scenery of Arizona.

This title gives you the most spectacular natural feature in the entire country - The Grand Canyon - you get to fly the ENTIRE Grand Canyon in photoreal detail.

Imagery is clear and crisp 50 cm source throughout for a stunningly realistic scenery.
